article.headline: Small scores 15 to help Army beat Holy Cross 70-57
article.description: — TJ Small scored 15 points as Army beat Holy Cross 70-57 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Small scores 15 to help Army beat Holy Cross 70-57
article.story: WEST POINT, N.Y. -- — TJ Small scored 15 points as Army beat Holy Cross 70-57 on Saturday. Small added six rebounds for the Black Knights (5-10, 1-1 Patriot League). Ryan Curry scored 13 points while shooting 4 for 10 (1 for 4 from 3-point range) and 4 of 4 from the free throw line, and added five rebounds and five assists. Josh Scovens was 3 of 13 shooting (1 for 7 from 3-point range) to finish with nine points. Will Batchelder led the way for the Crusaders (3-12, 0-2) with 16 points. Caleb Kenney added 14 points for Holy Cross. In addition, Joe Nugent had 11 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
